### 7. Academic Resources (Notes/Books/Questions)
# @name createNote
POST {{baseUrl}}/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Data Structures - Lecture 1",
    "subject": "CSE-101",
    "topic": "Linked Lists",
    "department_id": "{{departmentId}}",
    "university_id": "{{universityId}}",
    "download_url": "https://storage.example.com/notes/ds-l1.pdf"
}

### Filter Notes by Department and University
GET {{baseUrl}}/notes?university_id={{universityId}}&department_id={{departmentId}}

### Filter Books
GET {{baseUrl}}/books?university_id={{universityId}}

